{"tid":1919372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為英國建5G網路計劃被推翻！","createTime":"2020-03-10T17:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T05:40:59.000Z","uid":178187,"like":38,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1510c214f4e454855116f0029b6325244cb6f09c","tid":1919372,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"好彩仲有班議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3usAGT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3usAGT.png&h=a09d3c03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d276a8e8ddb156bfd6f786d5392759ba159d365","tid":1919372,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df662f4506991713309940e143ddbfc6d953642","tid":1919372,"uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"調轉下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a1c5b53c8a2395c94f713130292049468c59a0","tid":1919372,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/uk-politics-51806704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fuk-politics-51806704&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=22090257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/uk-politics-51806704</a><br />\n<br />\nThe government has defeated the first rebellion from its own MPs over plans to allow Huawei to be used in the UK's 5G mobile network.<br />\n<br />\nA number of senior Conservatives backed an amendment to end the Chinese firm's participation in the project by the start of 2023.<br />\n<br />\nDespite promises from the government of a new bill to address their concerns, rebel MPs pushed their plan to a vote.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">But with a large Commons majority, the government defeated it by 24 votes.</span><br />\n<br />\nCulture Minister Matt Warman said the government had heard the points &quot;loud and clear&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nHe added: &quot;We will now engage intensively with colleagues across the House to make sure that we will make out case at every possible level&hellip;and we will underline that we will always put national security at the very top of our agenda.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe use of Huawei technology in the 5G network was signed off by No 10 and security experts earlier this year, with the caveats of keeping the kit out of the most sensitive areas and capping its market share at 35%.<br />\n<br />\nBut Tory critics say the firm is an arm of the Chinese state and a risk to UK security - claims the firm rejects.<br />\n<br />\nOther countries, including the US and Australia, have banned Huawei from their own networks and criticised the UK's decision."},{"pid":"038b5b2d8068f413107d25aa6f8a38eb94f1401a","tid":1919372,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-51806704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-51806704&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=87adf2ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-51806704&h=be9ca867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-51806704</a><br />\n<br />\n求指點，究竟我地仲可以做到啲咩.......<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/699108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/699108</a><br />\n我終於知道你可以做D咩<br />\n番去讀書啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown